$NetBSD: patch-ab,v 1.16 2010/03/24 21:41:11 heinz Exp $

  - enable build of qmail-spamc
  - some files (local.cf, *.pre) are managed by pkgsrc, disable
    their installation.
  - pkgsrc creates B_DATADIR, so there is no need to re-set permissions

